	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have slowly been upgrading armor and working on stats.&nbsp;&nbsp;The great debate seems to be what stat(s) are the most important for accurate hitting?  I have my misses turned on as well as other's hits, and while I am currently wielding a slower 2hs item, my ghoulie seems to have the same problems with misses.  So, what stats are most important to correct this problem?  Dex??  Agi??  <br><br>I generally group with peeps about 5 lvls or so higher, I know that is a factor, but rangers and druids seems to be outhitting me, perhaps not on cumulative dmg but definitely on consistency.  I am boggled, and suggestions appreciated!<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
