	   <tr><td colspan=2>Two stats will help you.&nbsp;&nbsp;One you can directly affect, one you had better have up. *grin*<br><br>Strength will increase both your damage and accuracy.<br><br>Your weapon skill and Offense skill will, too.<br><br>Also, remember that a faster weapon allows more chances to hit, a slower weapon allows less.  Against mobs that have a lot of life, I'll switch to the GB because of those few extra hits I'll get, rather than the Messenger.<br><br>If anyone has anything to add, I'd love to know it, because I miss a lot too. *grin*<br>&nbsp;<br>Dalantia Dragonfury<br>Crusader of the Burning Heart, 60th Protection, Third Blessing<br>Fennin Ro<br>New Dawnings<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60479" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60479</a></td></tr>
