	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hail fellow paladins<br><br>I've been playinng EQ since July of this year and i'm currently lvl 47.&nbsp;&nbsp;As with most people I am never content with whatever armor i have and always looking for better upgrades.  I've made all the newbie mistakes and dont want to commit anymore now that i'm nearing the 50s.  here is a list of what I have on myself currently and I would definitely appreciate suggestions.  <br>DW Helm/blackened alloy coif<br>Sarnak hide mask<br>cougar claw earrings<br>spider fur collar/orc fang necklace<br>Rygorr battle mail<br>crystal chitin armplates<br>Obulus Death shroud<br>iceforgeshackles/rune mithril bracer<br>velium 6ac 65hp ring/velium fire emerald ring<br>silver chitin handwraps<br>TBB<br>Mithril greaves<br>crustacean boots<br>spider fur cloak<br>Right now I am trying to prepare myself for high level dungeons and I know that AC and resists are everything.  I'm not in an uber guild that raids ToV or go to planes on an everyday basis, but I do know that in order to join these uber guilds certain criteria must be met for example:  All resists must either be 80+ or better unbuffed.  My question is how do I get my stats up to that level without having to be in a super high guild???  What items are out there that will allow me to get my resist that high without sacrificing AC and stats?<br>&nbsp;<br>Furyon<br>59 Knight<br><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=605752" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=605752</a><br><br>Karana Server<br><br><br></td></tr>
