	   <tr><td colspan=2>Brother Hayle, I believe. He is in Splitpaw, and he is shut into a cell deep inside. Best bet for turning the parts in would be to bring a Wizard or Druid. Druid See Invis and Camo you and him/herself, then opens the door to Hayle's cell. You will have to drop invis to give Hayle the items, because you need better faction than Indiff. Once the transaction is complete, have the druid open the door and Evac you out (by this time, dropping invis will have gotten you a nice big Train, you don't want to be there when the train finds you :)<br><br>My 2cp.<br>&nbsp;<br>Balidin Evilbasher<br>60 Paladin<br>Xev</td></tr>
