	   <tr><td colspan=2>3 thing affect AC.<br>1. Hard AC - The AC listed on item.<br>2. Defense Skills<br>3. Agi - this is only a problem if you have below 75 getting it around 90 is good.<br><br>Now when you add hard Ac there is a converter that will convert your hard Ac to your soft Ac.&nbsp;&nbsp;Now adding 2 Ac at my lvl will add around 4 ish more Ac to my total. <br><br>Sorry i dont know the math. Maybe one of the more exp ppl could tell us?  *Cough* Pred =)<br><br>Amath<br>The Circle of Ten<br>&nbsp;<br>Amath<br>Paladin of The Circle of Ten {Bertoxx Server}</td></tr>
