	   <tr><td colspan=2>When looking at Armour. I follow these.<br>Ac - Your a tank firstly AC owns.<br>HP - Your going to get hit so having the HP to tank mobs till you can get a heal will help.<br>Resists - When you start fighing Mobs that start nukeing for like 200+ you will love your Resists.&nbsp;&nbsp;Resisting that nuke could be life or death.<br>Sta - Hp to some extent. At 60 i think 1 sta was about 4 hp.  <br>Str and other stats - Str is the easyest stat to get buffed. Druids/Shammies/Rangers all have Str buffs. and even enchanters have them to some extent.<br>Wis - Mana<br><br>Hope that helps a little..<br><br>Amath<br>&nbsp;<br>Amath<br>Paladin of The Circle of Ten {Bertoxx Server}</td></tr>
